ratings.comment: An amazing mentor that will help you with the transition to college life. He often talks about his experiences and will teach you ways to concentrate and destress. Since this is a seminar class, as long as you attend every class you will get full credits; and if you're lucky enough, he might even invite you to one of his productions and to dinner.

Doc is one of the best people in my life. He has helped me more than any of the professors at my previous high-ranking conservatory. He was there for me. Always. Learning to kinesthetically connect to my vertical potential has set me up for success, and I owe it all to Doc. Deuces.
